+// hash_set (SGI extension)
+
+#include <ext/hash_set>
+
+void
+test01()
+{
+  bool test = true;
+  const int werte[] = { 1, 25, 9, 16, -36};
+  const int anzahl = sizeof(werte) / sizeof(int);
+  __gnu_cxx::hash_set<int> intTable(werte, werte + anzahl);
+}
+
+int main()
+{
+  test01();
+  return 0;
+}
